{"tid":50053,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"[聖誕禮物] 年底前災情爆發？iPhone 7 Plus相機「黑畫面」激增!","createTime":"2016-12-22T06:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T06:09:24.000Z","uid":2339,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"002568e84ab8a1f99da736f9b5f91ff58bcd4df0","tid":50053,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T06:58:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://3c.ltn.com.tw/m/news/27928\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2F27928&d=U2Fvd7KZwp%2BnaqE9zEwOSmN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=216e6d7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2F3c.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2F27928&h=d960e920\" target=\"_blank\">http://3c.ltn.com.tw/m/news/27928</a><br />\n<br />\n儘管新手機上市或多或少都會有「災情」出現，但 Apple 這次卻相當反常地，在產品推出超過 2 個月後，才出現大量異常的狀況。這次災情的主角是 iPhone 7 系列手機，其中 iPhone 7 Plus 的異常狀況特別顯著！<br />\n<br />\n根據 Reddit 論壇上用戶的回報，已經有多名用戶的 iPhone 7 Plus 出現相機異常狀況，開啟後 Apple 相機或是第三方相機應用，全部都只會顯示一片黑畫面、而無法進行任何操作。<br />\n<br />\n科技網站《BGR》指出，這個狀況其實在先前就有出現過，但不知為何最近的回報狀況卻愈來愈多。除了黑畫面，iPhone 7 Plus 有時候拍攝畫面還會伴隨綠光或紫光，甚至會出現 iPhone 需要降溫的警告訊息。<br />\n<br />\n此外台灣也有不少 iPhone 7 用戶出現這類問題，目前已知的解決方案，是送交給 Apple 原廠維修，顯示應該是硬體問題。Apple 尚未對此公布專屬維修計畫，建議消費者可以主動聯繫 Apple 尋求維修細節。"},{"pid":"d0ef79064fd9c1f2143bd918671135b73aafc5d0","tid":50053,"uid":7886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T07:07:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d43a8acab20c30788f86572edf0336d018ab495","tid":50053,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T12:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/22/202535_e80e9129531dd66396f823c500ff009e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F22%2F202535_e80e9129531dd66396f823c500ff0